data.description: Great little house located directly across from Lake Challenger! This gem comes with impact windows, a tankless hot water heater, updated kitchen with tiled backsplash, and a top of the line, heavy gauged, standing seamed metal roof!  There is a screened patio with a utility room, a metal shed, carport, and additional storage adjacent to the shed.  Awesome back yard is fenced and cross fenced, so bring your pets!  There is additional concrete (85 ft long!)for your toys! Great location, close to parks, shopping, and more!
